{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"MediaQueryList.matches","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList/matches","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSS_Object_Model\">CSS Object Model</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList\"><code>MediaQueryList</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><em><code>matches</code></em></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList/media\"><code>media</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList/addListener\"><code>addListener()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList/removeListener\"><code>removeListener()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>事件</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList/change_event\"><code>change</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>继承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>CSSOM 的相关页面</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent\"><code>AnimationEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSS\"><code>CSS</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSConditionRule\"><code>CSSConditionRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSGroupingRule\"><code>CSSGroupingRule</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSKeyframeRule\"><code>CSSKeyframeRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSKeyframesRule\"><code>CSSKeyframesRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSMediaRule\"><code>CSSMediaRule</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSNamespaceRule\"><code>CSSNamespaceRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSPageRule\"><code>CSSPageRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSRule\"><code>CSSRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSRuleList\"><code>CSSRuleList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration\"><code>CSSStyleDeclaration</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleRule\"><code>CSSStyleRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleSheet\"><code>CSSStyleSheet</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSSupportsRule\"><code>CSSSupportsRule</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CaretPosition\"><code>CaretPosition</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Screen\"><code>Screen</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/StyleSheet\"><code>StyleSheet</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/StyleSheetList\"><code>StyleSheetList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TransitionEvent\"><code>TransitionEvent</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList\"><code>MediaQueryList</code></a> 接口的 <strong><code>matches</code></strong> 只读属性是一个布尔值，如果 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Document\"><code>document</code></a> 当前匹配媒体查询列表，该属性返回 <code>true</code>，否则返回 <code>false</code>。</p>\n<p>通过侦听发生在 <code>MediaQueryList</code> 的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList/change_event\" title=\"change\"><code>change</code></a> 事件，当 <code>matches</code> 的值发生变化时，你可以收到通知。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"值","title":"值","isH3":false,"content":"<p>一个布尔值，如果 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Document\"><code>document</code></a> 目前匹配媒体查询列表，该值为 <code>true</code>，反之为 <code>false</code>。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>该示例通过使用 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/@media/orientation\"><code>orientation</code></a> 媒体查询特性来创建一个媒体查询，以检测视口横纵方向的变化：</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">addMQListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">mq<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> callback</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>mq<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>addEventListener<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    mq<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"change\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> callback<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    mq<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>callback<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token function\">addMQListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">matchMedia</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"(orientation:landscape)\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token parameter\">event</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>matches<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n       <span class=\"token comment\">/* 现在是横向 */</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n       <span class=\"token comment\">/* 现在是纵向 */</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://drafts.csswg.org/cssom-view/#dom-mediaquerylist-matches","title":"CSSOM View Module"}],"query":"api.MediaQueryList.matches"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.MediaQueryList.matches","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList/matches/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见","title":"参见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/Media_Queries/Using_media